data.description: Little Deschutes River Front!! This Charming  3 bedroom 2 bath manufactured home sits on 1.2 acres with a detached Shop and carport. Very private location in the highly sought after Two Rivers North subdivision . Great river frontage. Subdivision is surrounded by forest land for your OHV adventures. Access from all 4 sides. Odell, Crescent and numerous other mountain lakes provide an unending amount of water activities. Willamette Pass Ski Resort and Pacific Crest Trail head within 15 minutes.This is a well cared for home.
